data.meta_description: 4 likes, 0 comments - prestonbj on May 25, 2024: "- 05.25.07 - 17 years ago today - we lost game show contestant/actor/comedian Charles Nelson Reilly. He was a staple on “Matchgame” and “The Tonight Show Starring Johnny Carson”. In his later years he took his comedic act on the road. He wasn’t ashamed of his ‘campy’ lifestyle. Audiences loved him! He passed away from complications of pneumonia. Charles Nelson Reilly was 76. - #charlesnelsonreilly - #matchgame - #thelifeofreilly".
